channel.title: Int Renamer (Renamed/Un-Renamed)
channel.description:
[center] Alright, just to clear up the biggest peice in here, Its Beta 0.6. All this is for is renaming, or un-renaming ints from some classes. Please note, it has a P for the icon, because i have my own programming website, its the logo i use for programs that i have made, deal with it. I know alot of people are doing to bitch now because there stuff can be stolen from re-named clients, but deal with it, what about you getting stuff from non-renamed?
UPDATE 1.5: Now does interfaces Custom renaming Option [/center]
It Renames/Un-Renames ints from the Following Classes [ul][*]ItemDef/Class8 [*]ObjectDef/Class46 [*]EntityDef/Class5 [*]Renaming Ints From Class9/RSInterface[/ul]
Working On: [ul][*]Outta Ideas, wanna name some?[/ul]
[center] Beta .6 [img]http://pic-host.netai.net/uploads/1261250341.png[/img]
Beta 1.5 [img]http://pic-host.netai.net/uploads/beta%201.5.PNG[/img]
DL: Sorry, my website was shutdown, until i get a new one, link wont be here. If someone wants to upload it to mediafire or something, i will rep++ you.
Got some suggestions? Post em, id be glad to hear as long as its not idiotic.
